    <p>We finally remark that the generated networks could be used within any multiscale simulation frameworks, in order to investigate, e.g., the processes of homeostasis and clonal expansion, as proposed in [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="CR35">35</xref>, <xref ref-type="bibr" rid="CR36">36</xref>].</p>
